I need to identify the profit an entity retains after all expenses have been deducted from total revenue.

Looking at the cash flow statement, the line item that represents this is "Net Profit" which is listed under "Cash Flow From Operating Activities". This represents the company's bottom line after accounting for all expenses.

In the given problem, the value for Net Profit is 1193771.08 as of 2024-01-28.
